Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.42,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord0\bord1\c&HE0CFC5&\fad(200,200)\pos(448,31)}非常感謝您使用NR 旅途中需要幫助 請到巢鴨站
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你急什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 佐為 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 你在吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 喂 佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這裏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 夠了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天和今天都跟著你團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在找什麼東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棋院裏沒有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋的事還是應該去棋院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棋院已經找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺家的倉庫裏也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 到底去哪裏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個 偶爾也去圍棋會場露露臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在為你加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底為了什麼去廣島的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚啊 不能早點回來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去的時候要先說清楚去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你可能有很多你自己的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 畢竟還只是個孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和周平那個人的對局還真累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋的事還是應該去棋院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去看一次試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光 等等 要去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棋院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃晚飯了 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點兒也不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前不久那傢伙在倉庫裏說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己即將消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐為竟然會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連想都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連想都沒想過！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼？ 這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是忘了東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是哪裏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼可能會出現的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼…鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棋院的建築物很古老了 現在又是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方都容易出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方說不定真的會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:11.44,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,GoGo圍棋教室
